## R and R studio

I have been gradually migrating from `Stata` to `R` because there exist many useful packages that facilitate both teaching and (reproducible) research in an elegant way. For example, this website is created completely using `Radix`, an `R` package built by Yihui Xie and his coauthors. Recently, I have also started to use `bookdown` to organize and write notes and papers. 

## Git and Github

Git and Github provide an important way for version control. 